* Update to version 24.3.3.dev1
Automatic release to 24.3.2

Add: delete_all on labels

Unlike the description says within set_all labels are not overriden but
labels that are not within the POST data but are on the PR stay.

For the use case that an action wants to override managed labels it
needs the possibility to delete previous labels.

For that the delete_all method is introduced.

Change: Document how to use shell command completion

Explain how to install the command completion for bash and zsh.

Automatic adjustments after release

* Update to version 24.2.3.dev1
Automatic release to 24.2.2

Only compile regex pattern once

Improve the performance for creating the regexp pattern by caching them.
With this change they will be created on demand once and afterwards they
are used from the cache.

Fix: Fix overriding company in copyright header via update-header CLI

We need a regex that matches all kind of company names not only
Greenbone. This also generalizes the code and makes update-header
independent of Greenbone specific use cases.
Add a test for updating a header with spdx copyright
Easier testing for update-header main function

Change: Allow to pass --year and --changed for update-header CLI

--year is the fallback of --changed if the year of the last git
modification can't be calculated. Therefore it should be allowed to be
set in conjunction with --changed.

Change: Improve help for update-header arguments

Improved usage and print also the defaults.
Add: Add test for update-header passing files and directories

Change: Improve and finalize update_file function API

Don't pass the cleanup_regexes to the function and instead just add a
flag to cleanup the updated file instead.
Remove obsolete Terminal mock class in update header test module

Use list and tuple instead of List and Tuple

List and Tuple are obsolete with PEP 585 and Python 3.9.

Use list comprehension for _compile_outdated_regex

For easy iterations that create a list from a list it's better to use
list comprehension and also it should be faster.

Simplify _get_exclude_list

It's more likely that the exclude file doesn't exist. Therefore it is
better to check is the file exists then reacting on the file not found
exception.

Change: Remove copyright_regex from update_header function

The update_header function just expect a year, license and company name
at the end.
